# puppet apply

> Apply Puppet manifests locally
> More information: https://puppet.com/docs/puppet/7/man/apply.html

- Apply a manifest:

`puppet apply {string value: path/to/manifest}`

- Execute puppet code:

`puppet apply --execute {string value: code}`

- Use a specific module and hiera config file:

`puppet apply --modulepath {directory value} --hiera_config {file value} {string value: path/to/manifest}`
